file.name: api.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
components:
  schemas:
    DuplicatesParent:
      allOf:
        - $ref: '#/components/schemas/ContainsNestedAnyOfWithDupes'
        - type: object
          properties:
            top_level_duplicate:
              type: number

    ContainsNestedAnyOfWithDupes:
      anyOf:
        - $ref: "#/components/schemas/FirstOneD"
        - $ref: "#/components/schemas/FirstOneD"
        - $ref: "#/components/schemas/TheDuplicator"

    FirstOneD:
      type: object
      properties:
        child_duplicate:
          type: string

    TheDuplicator:
      type: object
      properties:
        top_level_duplicate:
          type: string
        child_duplicate:
          type: string
